languages.text: "Раз наша встреча все же состоялась, то мои дела здесь закончены. Я достаточно долго пробыл в {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}реальном мире{/g} — пришла пора прощаться".

traits.locale_text: "Я достаточно долго был в реальном мире — пришла пора прощаться. Сыны и дочери Опустошительной бури — я оставляю этого мон-кай вам. Развлекайтесь".

languages.text: "Now that our meeting has taken place, my business here is done. I have spent enough time in {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}realspace{/g}, and it is time to bid you goodbye."
languages.original_text: "Раз наша встреча все же состоялась, то мои дела здесь закончены. Я достаточно долго пробыл в {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}реальном мире{/g} — пришла пора прощаться".

traits.locale_text: "I have spent enough time in realspace — it is time to bid you goodbye. Sons and daughters of the Reaving Tempest — I leave this mon-keigh to you. Enjoy yourselves."

languages.text: 「お前と会えた。俺のここでの用事は終わりだ。{g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}リアルスペース{/g}で過ごしすぎたようだ。そろそろお別れだな」
languages.original_text: "Now that our meeting has taken place, my business here is done. I have spent enough time in {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}realspace{/g}, and it is time to bid you goodbye."

traits.locale_text: 「{g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}リアルスペース{/g}はもう飽きた。そろそろ別れの時間だ。略奪の嵐の息子と娘たちよ――このモン＝ケイの運命はお前たちの手に委ねる。思いきり楽しみたまえ」

languages.text: “既然我们已经见了面，那我在这里的事情也就办完了。我在{g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}真实世界{/g}中已经呆得太久了，是时候和你说再见了。”
languages.original_text: "Now that our meeting has taken place, my business here is done. I have spent enough time in {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}realspace{/g}, and it is time to bid you goodbye."

languages.text: « Maintenant que nous nous sommes vus, plus rien ne me retient ici. J'ai passé bien assez de temps dans l'{g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}espace réel{/g}, et il est temps pour moi de vous dire adieu. »
languages.original_text: "Now that our meeting has taken place, my business here is done. I have spent enough time in {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}realspace{/g}, and it is time to bid you goodbye."

languages.text: «Ahora que nuestro encuentro ha tenido lugar, mis asuntos aquí han terminado. Ya llevo suficiente tiempo en el {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}espacio real{/g}, así que adiós».
languages.original_text: "Now that our meeting has taken place, my business here is done. I have spent enough time in {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}realspace{/g}, and it is time to bid you goodbye."

languages.text: "Nun, da unser Treffen stattgefunden hat, ist meine Arbeit hier getan. Ich war lange genug im {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}Realraum{/g}, es wird Zeit, mich zu verabschieden."

languages.text: "Görüşmemiz sonlandığına göre buradaki işim bitmiş demektir. {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}Gerçekuzay{/g} düzleminde yeterince vakit harcadım, veda etme zamanı."

traits.locale_text: "Görüşmemiz sonlandığına göre buradaki işim de bitmiş demektir. {g|Encyclopedia:Realspace}Gerçekuzay{/g} düzleminde yeterince vakit harcadım, veda edeyim artık."
